sequenceDiagram
    participant R as RebalanceImpl
    participant P as PullMessageService
    participant D as DefaultMQPushConsumerImpl
    participant B as Broker PullMessageProcessor
    participant H as PullRequestHoldService
    participant Q as 本地 ProcessQueue
    participant E as ConsumeMessageService

    R->>D: 分配 MessageQueue，创建 ProcessQueue
    P->>D: 执行 pullMessage
    D->>B: Pull(queueId, nextOffset, batchSize)
    alt 有消息
        B-->>D: 消息批次 + nextBeginOffset
    else 暂无消息且允许挂起
        B->>H: 保存长轮询请求
        H-->>B: 新消息到达或超时后唤醒
        B-->>D: 消息或空结果
    end
    D->>Q: putMessage
    Q->>E: 提交并发/顺序消费任务
    E->>E: 执行业务 Listener
    E->>D: 更新并持久化消费位点
    D->>P: 调度下一次 Pull
